Binary release

  Download the Asciidoc Maven Plugin binary release 
{{{http://maven.r-w-x.net/releases/net/rwx/asciidoc/asciidoc-maven-plugin/${project.version}/asciidoc-maven-plugin-${project.version}.jar}asciidoc-maven-plugin-${project.version}.jar}}

  The binary release can be manually installed using this command :

+----------------------------------------
mvn install:install-file 
    -Dfile=path/to/mly/asciidoc-maven-plugin-${project.version}.jar
    -DgroupId=jnet.rwx.asciidoc -DartifactId=asciidoc-maven-plugin 
    -Dversion=${project.version} -Dpackaging=jar
+----------------------------------------

